===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|nl|/ɦɛi̯/}}
* {{audio|nl|Nl-hij.ogg|audio}}
* {{hyphenation|nl|hij}}
* {{rhymes|nl|ɛi̯}}
* {{homophones|nl|hei}}

===Pronoun===
{{head|nl|pronoun}}

# ''Third-person singular, masculine, subjective:'' [[he]].
#: {{ux|nl|'''Hij''' loopt.|'''He''' walks.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|nl|De tafel is duur omdat '''hij''' van glas is gemaakt.|The table is expensive because '''it''' is made of glass.}}

====Usage notes====
* When the word occurs other than as the first word of a clause and is not emphatically stressed, it is usually pronounced as {{IPAchar|/i/}}. This is a completely accepted pronunciation in standard speech.
* The word can also be used to refer to inanimate nouns of the feminine gender.

